short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Curate to Frameboard Chrome extension allows you to curate anything on the web with one click.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Select the Frameboard button on any web page, choose the image you want to curate, select your board, instantly capture the title and description, and view your curation on your board.

You can also use Curate to Frameboard as a handy way to visit your Frameboard profile.

Send feedback to jayme@launcher.xyz or @jaymehoffman on telegram.
